Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: The Monica Lewinsky scandal emerges
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yjflj
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 30 Jan 1998
Tapes emerge alledging that Monica Lewinsky was asked to lie on oath about an affair with the President and Clinton delivers a dazzling state of the Union address.